refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public stringQuickHashStringIntHash::saveToString
This method returns a serialized version of the hash in the same format that loadFromString() can read.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 This method returns a serialized format of an existing hash, in the same format
 that loadFromString() can read.

  &reftitle.examples;



    QuickHashStringIntHash::saveToString example


<?php
$hash = new QuickHashStringIntHash( 1024 );
var_dump( $hash->add( "fourty three", 42 ) );
var_dump( $hash->add( "fifty two", 52 ) );

var_dump( $hash->saveToString() );
?>
